<%- | String $host, Integer $port | -%>
# Managed by Puppet - syslog_forward module. Do not edit manually.
# Forwards all syslog to the central receiver via TCP with an in-memory
# queue to buffer messages if the receiver is temporarily unreachable.
# "& stop" halts further rsyslog processing after the forward, preventing
# local writes to /var/log/syslog etc. (file must load before 50-default.conf).
*.* action(type="omfwd" target="<%= $host %>" port="<%= $port %>" protocol="tcp" action.resumeRetryCount="-1" queue.type="linkedList" queue.size="10000")
& stop
